creator: Tapps Games
descriptionHtml:
What’s the wisest animal species on Earth? Mice, obviously!

Combine different mouse species in innovative experiments and create new mutant mice that will keep on absorbing all that scientific knowledge firsthand!

Make a mouse that likes to stand beside computers, rats that will travel overseas in search of a better life, rodents so smart they become famous chefs and the face of billionaire media empires...

Whichever mouse you choose to create, though, keep in mind they’re creatures with feelings.

So be mice!


MOUSEY FEATURES

🐭Pantheon: a new place for supreme beings to look down on us mortals and laugh at our misery
🐭Impostors: watch out for impostors trying to steal the spotlight from the mice!

HOW TO PLAY

🐭Drag and drop similar mice to create new mutant creatures
🐭Use mouse eggs to earn coins, buy new creatures and make even more money
🐭Alternatively, fiercely tap a mouse to make coins pop from their eggs

HIGHLIGHTS

🐭Different stages and many rat species to discover
🐭A mind-blowing story with mousey twists!
🐭The unexpected mix of alpaca-like evolution and incremental clicker games
🐭Doodle-like illustrations
🐭Open-ended gameplay: enjoy the freedom!
🐭No mice were harmed in the making of this game, only developers

Now this is what your grandpa would call a rattling good game!

Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.

Combine different mouse species in innovative experiments and create new mutant mice that will keep on absorbing all that scientific knowledge firsthand!

Make a mouse that likes to stand beside computers, rats that will travel overseas in search of a better life, rodents so smart they become famous chefs and the face of billionaire media empires...

Whichever mouse you choose to create, though, keep in mind they’re creatures with feelings.

So be mice!


MOUSEY FEATURES

🐭Pantheon: a new place for supreme beings to look down on us mortals and laugh at our misery
🐭Impostors: watch out for impostors trying to steal the spotlight from the mice!

HOW TO PLAY

🐭Drag and drop similar mice to create new mutant creatures
🐭Use mouse eggs to earn coins, buy new creatures and make even more money
🐭Alternatively, fiercely tap a mouse to make coins pop from their eggs

HIGHLIGHTS

🐭Different stages and many rat species to discover
🐭A mind-blowing story with mousey twists!
🐭The unexpected mix of alpaca-like evolution and incremental clicker games
🐭Doodle-like illustrations
🐭Open-ended gameplay: enjoy the freedom!
🐭No mice were harmed in the making of this game, only developers

Now this is what your grandpa would call a rattling good game!

Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.
